snippet.title: EVE Galaxy Conquest - Discovery
snippet.description:
From the creators of acclaimed MMO EVE Online, prepare to enter the vast cosmos of New Eden where intense factional warfare and diplomacy will force you to consider every decision, find allies, and outsmart your foes in a battle for seasonal supremacy.

Official Website: https://www.evegalaxyconquest.com/

FOLLOW OUR SOCIALS
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/playEVEGalaxyConquest
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Galaxy_Conquest/
Discord: www.discord.gg/galaxyconquest
